snippet.title: GTA Online: A Safehouse in the Hills Coming December 10
snippet.description:
A Safehouse in the Hills, the monumental new GTA Online update, arrives on December 10.

For those who have reached the highest rungs of the criminal ladder, celebrate your triumph with a painstakingly crafted palace in one of Los Santos’ most exclusive neighborhoods, complete with breathtaking views, the finest amenities, and countless ways to customize and make it your own.

Plus, an all-new action-packed adventure — along with exquisite new vehicles to collect, the return of a familiar face, and much more.

snippet.title: India’s Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas — ‘Sholay - The Final Cut’ 12th Dec release worldwide
snippet.description:
India’s Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas — ‘Sholay - The Final Cut’ 12th Dec release worldwide

Presenting the trailer of Sholay: The Final Cut.
Restored in 4K & Dolby 5.1, and releasing on 12th December 2025, this is the first-ever theatrical presentation of the original uncut version. As we celebrate 50 years of Sholay, we are honoured to bring this timeless classic back to cinemas for audiences old and new.

Produced by Sippy Films · Directed by Ramesh Sippy · Restored by Film Heritage Foundation
Releasing theatrically via PEN Marudhar.

#SholayTheFinalCut #SholayOn12Dec #SholayTrailer

Film: Sholay (1975) | शोले
Film cast : Amitabh Bachchan, Dharmendra, Hema Malini, Sanjeev Kumar, Amjad Khan, Jaya Bachchan, A K Hangal, Satyen Kappu, Mac Mohan, Sachin Pilgaonkar, Jagdeep, Asrani, Leela Mishra, Iftekhar, Om Shiv Puri, Viju Khote, Vikas Anand, Keshto Mukherjee, Mushtaq Merchant, Gita Siddharth, Helen, Jalal Aga, Birbal, Jairaj, Master Alankar, Raj Kishore, Sharad Kumar, Bhanumati, Rajesh, Darshan, Rajan Kapoor, Habib, Surender, Bhagwan Sinha, Jerry Dsouza, Kedar, Saigal, Rajeshwari, Krishna, Girija
Singer : Anand Bakshi, Bhupinder, Kishore Kumar, Lata Mangeshkar, Manna Dey, R D Burman
Lyricist : Anand Bakshi
Music Director : R D Burman, Basu Manohari, Maruti Rao
Film Director : Ramesh Sippy
Film Producer : G P Sippy

 In the village of Ramgarh, retired police chief Thakur Baldev Singh (Sanjeev Kumar) plots to bring down the notorious bandit Gabbar Singh (Amjad Khan) and enlists the help of two lesser criminals, Jai (Amitabh Bachchan) and Veeru (Dharmendra). When Gabbar attacks the village, however, Jai and Veeru wonder why Thakur does nothing to help them. They soon learn that he has no arms, and that Gabbar was the one who cut them off. Enraged by this, they redouble their efforts to help.

snippet.title: Robosen's Transformers Soundwave Robot - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a look at the Robosen's Transformers Soundwave robot trailer for the latest Transformers robot from the team at Robosen in collaboration with Hasbro. The trailer gives a deep dive into Robosen's Soundwave's features. Soundwave is a fully auto-converting robot, and this Decepticon spy comes to life with cutting-edge technology and a nostalgic design, including life-like actions and sinister commands. Soundwave is also a functional Bluetooth speaker while in cassette mode, with the ability to stream music, with skip through, pause, and play all with Soundwave's front facing retro tape deck buttons. There is also an integrated recording feature. The original G1 voice of Soundwave, Frank Welker, returns with over 200+ recorded lines for Robosen's Soundwave. Robosen's Soundwave also includes articulating hip-joints, 84 high-performance chipsets and 28 precision-built servo motors. 

Robosen’s Flagship Soundwave, the second Decepticon collectible within the range, is now available for pre-order at Robosen.com and will soon be available on HasbroPulse.com, and will retail on pre-sale for $999 USD for a 30-day window before moving to its standard price of $1,399.

snippet.title: Digimon Story Time Stranger | Season Pass DLC Alternate Dimension Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Your mission is to defeat the Digimon responsible for this Akashic Backdoor.

Additional Digimon & Episode Pack 1: Alternate Dimension is available December 8th at 3PM PST | 6PM EST for Digimon Story Time Stranger!

Travel across time and parallel worlds in the turn-based RPG Digimon Story Time Stranger – available now on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and Steam! Get it today: www.bnent.eu/DigimonStory-TS

The Deluxe Edition includes the base game, plus Costume: Cyber Sleuth Set and the Season Pass featuring 3 DLC releases.
The Ultimate Edition includes Early Unlock for a special Agumon and special Gabumon with their Digivolution conditions already unlocked. The fastest way to get your hands on Agumon (Bond of Bravery) and Gabumon (Bond of Friendship)! Packed with a Season Pass, exclusive costumes, bonus items, and a nostalgic Cyber Sleuth BGM Pack—this is the definitive way to experience your Digimon adventure.
